Serialized Form

  • Package com.shouldis.bitset

    • Class com.shouldis.bitset.BitSet extends java.lang.Object implements Serializable

      serialVersionUID:
      1L

      • Serialized Fields

        • size
          int size
          The number of indices accessible by this BitSet. Indices 0 through size -1 are accessible.
        • wordCount
          int wordCount
          The number of long words contained by this BitSet. Equal to ceiling(BitSet.size / 64) and BitSet.words.length.
        • words
          long[] words
          Array holding the long words whose bits are manipulated. Has length ceiling(BitSet.size / 64). Though this has protected visibility, using methods such as BitSet.getWord(int), BitSet.setWord(int, long), BitSet.andWord(int, long) is preferred over direct access.

      serialVersionUID:
      1L

    • Class com.shouldis.bitset.matrix.Matrix extends java.lang.Object implements Serializable

      serialVersionUID:
      1L

      • Serialized Fields

        • bits
          BitSet bits
          The BitSet storing the bits contained in this BitSet. (X, Y) coordinates are mapped to indices through Matrix.index(int, int).
